title: Standing Desk Review: Varidesk Pro Vs. Victor DC350 Standing Desk
description:
This video, features two different standing desks - the Victor DC350  and the Varidesk Pro 36. A clear winner is revealed in this head to head comparison. Be sure to review all your options when considering a standing desk. 

Victor DC350 Standing Desk: https://www.victortech.com/category/sit-to-stand-desks
